lity is only available for 1 time in 3 years duration.Moreover, applicant must be a resident of Haryana.Cycle Yojana Eligibility Haryana LabourThe eligibility criteria for Cycle Yojana of Haryana Labour Department is mentioned in the table below:-Eligibility CriteriaMembership Years / \u0938\u0926\u0938\u094d\u092f\u0924\u093e \u0935\u0930\u094d\u09371Apply Frequency / \u0906\u0935\u0947\u0926\u0928 \u0915\u0940 \u0938\u0940\u092e\u093e1Scheme For / \u0907\u0938 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090fAllContinue After Death / \u092e\u0943\u0924\u094d\u092f\u0941 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0926 \u091c\u093e\u0930\u0940NoFor more details contact the Haryana Labour Welfare Board : 0172-2560226, Bays No. 29-30 (Pocket-II), Sector-04, Panchkula (Haryana) \u2013 134112, contact number : 1800-180-2129 (Toll Free Number), head office : 0172-2701373, IT Cell: 0172-2971057.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: hrylabour.gov.in  at  "}